      "writtenOn": "2020-12-07T19:10:41Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I\u0027m experimenting with an internalQuickReject(const SkRect\u0026 bounds, const SkPaint\u0026 paint, const SkMatrix* \u003d nullptr). That plus some paint canonizing for the drawPoints/drawVertices/drawImages should let everyone go through this function. The paint canonizing will be another CL that will come first.",
