      "writtenOn": "2020-12-07T19:33:42Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This sounds good to me, though I think I\u0027d first try just plain copy instead of copy-on-write?  In general I want to swing way in favor of simple correct code in SkCanvas unless we\u0027ve got a profile saying it\u0027s necessary.",
      "parentUuid": "272c64f2_5d020fe3",
      "revId": "70b0c520af88e5b162a5f23d73f19e7b4db8f513",
